data.description: Wonderfully updated farmhouse chic home on large lot with huge covered patio! Terrific location just minutes from Alliance shopping and dining, Tanger outlets, Texas Motor Speedway, and easy access to Denton and Fort Worth. Do not miss the newer flooring throughout, custom accents and lighting, the exquisite master suite with separate vanities, separate shower, and soaker tub! Full-featured home comes with office or fourth bedroom, open concept island to enjoy breakfast or entertaining, large backyard covered patio with grill, and so much more! Do not miss this gem and HUGE lot for the area
